io.jenetics.xml

Class Readers.LongChromosome

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.jenetics.xml.Readers.LongChromosome
  • Enclosing class:
    Readers

    public static final class Readers.LongChromosome
extends Object
    Reader methods for LongChromosome objects.

    XML format 

     
 <long-chromosome length="3">
     <min>-9223372036854775808</min>
     <max>9223372036854775807</max>
     <alleles>
         <allele>-1345217698116542402</allele>
         <allele>-7144755673073475303</allele>
         <allele>6053786736809578435</allele>
     </alleles>
 </long-chromosome>
